{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in 'Tales of Terror'\u2014keep it in your Wishlist and follow along as frequent updates transform this game into a uniquely special, terrifying, and thrilling experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/HeaderWishlist.gif?t=1728315606\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an unforgettable journey into the unknown with 'Tales of Terror'! Brace yourself for a gripping PVE experience that not only pushes the boundaries of fear but invites you to share the thrills with friends in an immersive co-op adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/PLCoopGif.gif?t=1728315606\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc65 <strong>Cooperative Horror:</strong> Team up with friends in heart-pounding 4-player cooperative gameplay. Face the terror together, or go solo if you dare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udddf\u200d\u2642\ufe0f <strong>Monstrous Outbreak:</strong> Explore a desolate science research facility overrun by a nightmarish outbreak. Confront mutated horrors, solve mysteries, and survive the relentless onslaught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd75\ufe0f <strong>Solo Survival:</strong> For the brave souls who prefer to go it alone, solo play offers a unique and intense survival experience. Can you navigate the twisted corridors and unravel the dark secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf10 <strong>Uncover the Unknown:</strong> Dive into a narrative-rich horror adventure that challenges your wits and survival instincts. Uncover the secrets hidden within the corrupted facility and face the horrors that lurk in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to confront the nightmares that await? Gather your courage, assemble your team, or brave the darkness alone. Tales of Terror awaits, and the horror has evolved. Will you survive the SRF Labs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1824150/extras/ssGifHeader.gif?t=1728315606\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Kill the Crawlers!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/7e13041487403bae25a8cae15f5d64dc9aea7b54.jpg"},{"name":"Axe to the Back ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/21bd5a98c66a1eff927d97765c09552cc972a69c.jpg"},{"name":"Begone Demon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/dbbecbc0c766ee762b0f62eb6b81635473890390.jpg"},{"name":"Hold the Door ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/848cd075775eabd6ac9a63343938853551f86e4c.jpg"},{"name":"Hacker ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/752675890e764effa42f5e167db955fe36ea5520.jpg"},{"name":"Lifeline ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/225bdcc5d4b06f1fafb28dab45646ddcf5acd886.jpg"},{"name":"Into the dungeon ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/f890e2157cd091b5896fa4bad04be567b4cdb3d0.jpg"},{"name":"Crawl with Me ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/83d95bce094b2cbd99c2d037dc6841d6ebdae66d.jpg"},{"name":"Mauled Alive! ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1824150/f5f56a805f9810e084e0d8c996d6bb3bab1a1b48.jpg"},{